%N A157452 Number generated by regarding the numbers in row n of A003983 as digits of a base n number.
%C A157452 We are regarding A003983 as a triangle, not as an array by antidiagonals.
%F A157452 t(n,m)=Min[1 + m, 1 + (n - m)]; a(n)=FromDigits[{Table[t[n, m], {m, 0, n}], n + 1}, n + 1].
%e A157452 Row 4 of A003983 is 1,2,2,1. The number 1221 in base 4 is 4^3 + 2*4^2 + 2*4 + 1 = 105, so a(4) = 105.
%t A157452 t[n_, m_] =Min[m, n - m + 1];
